if cmd: is recieved state is COMMAND and exit detection
else continue
send a "*"
if serial data is recieved
then check each line for the text PK-232
if PK-232 is found mode is AUTOBAUD
then keep reading until "cmd:" appears (banner terminator)
and only then exit detection
else continue
send the following hex bytes $01 $01 $4F $48 $4F $4E $17
send return
if cmd: is recieved state is HOSTMODE and exit detection
else continue
